---
import { processSteps } from "../../data/siteConfig";
import { ChevronDown, ArrowRight, ArrowDown } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container space-y-16">
    {/* Part A: Personal Branding & Accordion Dropdown */}
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] gap-10 xl:gap-16 items-center"
    >
      {/* Left Column: Portrait Image Card */}
      <div
        class="relative w-full max-w-[360px] md:max-w-[400px] aspect-[4/5] mx-auto lg:mr-auto rounded-2xl border border-white/8 bg-brand-card p-3.5 shadow-[0_15px_35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-coral/30 reveal-on-scroll-left"
      >
        {/* User Profile Image */}
        <img
          src="/assets/foto/foto_me.jpeg"
          alt="Sanzzyy Profile"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl transition-all duration-300"
          loading="lazy"
        />

        {/* Overlapping Floating Badge (Name Card) */}
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 px-5 py-3.5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl bg-brand-bg/90 backdrop-blur-md flex flex-col gap-0.5 shadow-2xl"
        >
          <h4
            class="m-0 text-white font-satoshi font-bold text-[15.5px] tracking-wide"
          >
            Sanzzyy
          </h4>
          <p
            class="m-0 text-brand-gold font-inter text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
          >
            Fullstack Developer
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Right Column: Interactive Dropdown / Accordion */}
      <div 
        class="grid justify-items-start text-left w-full reveal-on-scroll"
      >
        <p class="section-kicker">Meet The Creator</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading-h2">
          Membangun Kepercayaan Lewat Keahlian Personal
        </h2>
        <p class="section-heading-p mb-7">
          Di balik Syzen Web, ada dedikasi personal untuk membantu bisnis Anda
          tampil menonjol. Kami memadukan visi desain yang kuat dengan kode
          berkualitas tinggi untuk menciptakan website berkinerja tinggi.
        </p>

        {/* Details Dropdowns Accordion */}
        <div class="space-y-3.5 w-full">
          {/* Item 1 */}
          <details
            class="group border border-white/8 rounded-xl bg-brand-card overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 open:border-brand-coral/30 open:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
            open
          >
            <summary
              class="flex items-center justify-between p-4.5 cursor-pointer list-none select-none text-white hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3.5">
                <span
                  class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-sm md:text-base font-satoshi"
                  >01</span
                >
                <span
                  class="font-bold text-[14px] md:text-[15.5px] font-satoshi tracking-wide"
                  >Siapa di Balik Syzen Web?</span
                >
              </div>
              <span
                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-coral shrink-0"
              >
                <ChevronDown className="w-5 h-5" strokeWidth={2.5} />
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="accordion-grid-wrapper border-t border-white/4">
              <div class="accordion-grid-inner">
                <div
                  class="px-4.5 pb-4.5 pt-4 text-slate-300 text-[13.8px] md:text-[14.5px] leading-relaxed font-inter"
                >
                  Halo, saya Muhammad Sajid Izzulhaq. Berbekal latar belakang di
                  bidang Teknik Informatika, fokus utama saya adalah membantu
                  pemilik UMKM dan bisnis lokal untuk melangkah ke dunia digital.
                  Saya percaya bahwa website yang baik bukan sekadar tampil
                  menarik, tapi harus bisa menjadi solusi yang memudahkan
                  operasional dan mendukung pertumbuhan bisnis Anda.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          {/* Item 2 */}
          <details
            class="group border border-white/8 rounded-xl bg-brand-card overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 open:border-brand-coral/30 open:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
          >
            <summary
              class="flex items-center justify-between p-4.5 cursor-pointer list-none select-none text-white hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3.5">
                <span
                  class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-sm md:text-base font-satoshi"
                  >02</span
                >
                <span
                  class="font-bold text-[14px] md:text-[15.5px] font-satoshi tracking-wide"
                  >Komitmen & Pendekatan Kerja</span
                >
              </div>
              <span
                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-coral shrink-0"
              >
                <ChevronDown className="w-5 h-5" strokeWidth={2.5} />
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="accordion-grid-wrapper border-t border-white/4">
              <div class="accordion-grid-inner">
                <div
                  class="px-4.5 pb-4.5 pt-4 text-slate-300 text-[13.8px] md:text-[14.5px] leading-relaxed font-inter"
                >
                  Saya mengedepankan komunikasi yang transparan, ramah, dan
                  kolaboratif. Bekerja sama dengan saya berarti Anda berdiskusi
                  langsung dengan pengembangnya. Saya siap mendengarkan visi
                  bisnis Anda, menjelaskan hal teknis dengan bahasa yang mudah
                  dipahami, dan memastikan website selesai tepat waktu sesuai
                  kebutuhan.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          {/* Item 3 */}
          <details
            class="group border border-white/8 rounded-xl bg-brand-card overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 open:border-brand-coral/30 open:shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
          >
            <summary
              class="flex items-center justify-between p-4.5 cursor-pointer list-none select-none text-white hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3.5">
                <span
                  class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-sm md:text-base font-satoshi"
                  >03</span
                >
                <span
                  class="font-bold text-[14px] md:text-[15.5px] font-satoshi tracking-wide"
                  >Teknologi Modern & Speed</span
                >
              </div>
              <span
                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-coral shrink-0"
              >
                <ChevronDown className="w-5 h-5" strokeWidth={2.5} />
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="accordion-grid-wrapper border-t border-white/4">
              <div class="accordion-grid-inner">
                <div
                  class="px-4.5 pb-4.5 pt-4 text-slate-300 text-[13.8px] md:text-[14.5px] leading-relaxed font-inter"
                >
                  Kami membangun web menggunakan tumpukan teknologi modern
                  berkecepatan tinggi seperti Astro, React, dan Tailwind CSS.
                  Hasilnya adalah website statis super ringan, SEO ramah mesin
                  pencari, serta integrasi tombol Call-to-Action WhatsApp yang
                  sangat responsif.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Part B: Workflow / Process Grid */}
    <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/8">
      <div 
        class="max-w-[760px] mb-10 reveal-on-scroll"
      >
        <p class="section-kicker">Our Workflow</p>
        <h3
          class="text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl font-satoshi font-bold leading-tight"
        >
          Alur Kerja yang Transparan & Terarah
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-5 xl:gap-6 w-full"
      >
        {
          processSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <article 
              class="relative grid gap-2.5 align-content-start p-5 border border-white/6 rounded-xl bg-brand-card/80 backdrop-blur-md shadow-[0_10px_28px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-coral/30 hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(255,101,63,0.08)] group reveal-on-scroll"
              style={`transition-delay: ${index * 80}ms;`}
            >
              {/* Card Header: Number Badge and Title side-by-side to maximize space */}
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3.5 mb-1 shrink-0">
                <span class="w-8.5 h-8.5 rounded-full bg-brand-coral/10 border border-brand-coral/25 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-coral font-satoshi font-extrabold text-[14px] shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(255,101,63,0.1)] shrink-0">
                  {step.number}
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[14.5px] sm:text-[15px] font-bold leading-snug font-satoshi tracking-wide group-hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors duration-200">
                  {step.title}
                </h3>
              </div>

              {/* Card Description */}
              <p class="m-0 text-slate-300 text-[13px] sm:text-[13.5px] leading-relaxed font-inter">
                {step.description}
              </p>

              {/* Connector Arrows (Visual Pathway Route) placed directly under article to center vertically */}
              {index === 0 && (
                <>
                  {/* Desktop & Tablet: Horizontal arrow centered vertically in the middle of the card side */}
                  <div
                    class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2 left-full w-6 lg:w-5 xl:w-6 h-8 z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowRight
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                  {/* Mobile: Vertical arrow pointing down under the bottom center of the card */}
                  <div
                    class="sm:hidden absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-full h-6 flex items-center justify-center z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowDown
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                </>
              )}

              {index === 1 && (
                <>
                  {/* Desktop: Horizontal arrow pointing right */}
                  <div
                    class="hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2 left-full w-5 xl:w-6 h-8 z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowRight
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                  {/* Tablet: Vertical arrow pointing down for 2-column wrapping */}
                  <div
                    class="hidden sm:flex lg:hidden absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-full h-6 flex items-center justify-center z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowDown
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                  {/* Mobile: Vertical arrow pointing down */}
                  <div
                    class="sm:hidden absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-full h-6 flex items-center justify-center z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowDown
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                </>
              )}

              {index === 2 && (
                <>
                  {/* Desktop & Tablet: Horizontal arrow pointing right */}
                  <div
                    class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2 left-full w-6 lg:w-5 xl:w-6 h-8 z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowRight
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                  {/* Mobile: Vertical arrow pointing down */}
                  <div
                    class="sm:hidden absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-full h-6 flex items-center justify-center z-20 pointer-events-none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <ArrowDown
                      className="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold"
                      strokeWidth={3.2}
                    />
                  </div>
                </>
              )}
            </article>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
